            <item>
               <ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="ref32">V. Writings and Printed Material</ref>
            </item>
         </list>
         <p>A very complete run of manuscript sermons provides excellent documentation of the theology and work of a Congregational minister during the second half of the nineteenth century.</p>  
